  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Rooms</strong> are <span>19 - 24m² and have been</span> finished in a contemporary style with views towards the mountains. Facilities include a balcony, air conditioning, TV, wifi, minibar, tea &amp; coffee making facilities and a safe. They can sleep up to three adults and are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Sea View Rooms</strong> offer the same amenities as above but have lovely sea views from the balcony. They can sleep up to three adults and are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Executive Rooms</strong> are <span>45 - 50m² and are </span>located between the third and seventh floors of the hotel with spectacular views across the Bay of Naples. Guests in these room types also have access to the roof terrace with plunge pool and Settimo Lounge Bar where you can enjoy complimentary drinks and snacks.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
